Key Match Events: Kylian Mbappé scored a goal in the 85th minute.
Randal Kolo Muani scored a header in the 43rd minute.
Jonathan Clauss scored a goal in the 70th minute.
Post-Match Reflections: Didier Deschamps praised Kylian Mbappé, calling him a great leader and emphasizing the need for him to be at his best.
Deschamps also praised N'Golo Kante for his solid performance, stating 'He did himself proud.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Saint-Symphorien Stadium in Longeville-les-Metz, eastern France.
France received hearty support at the match.
